  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>FastPack</i> <i>- Quick Delivery Training Program</i> is a fast paced game where you deliver packages to the correct adress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697540/extras/2109030245f6fdbe8fe7775f9cdcf7d0.poster.avif?t=1751833217\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697540/extras/2109030245f6fdbe8fe7775f9cdcf7d0.webm?t=1751833217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced package delivery</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive around in a small open world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to strange NPC's</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise your profile</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn a Diploma you can print out and put next to your CV</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade mode:</strong> Deliver packages as fast as possible in a race against the clock. Gain more time by delivering more packages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Contract Mode:</strong> Walk around without time constraint. Complete contracts to gain Money. Contracts are small missions, for example \"Deliver 20 packages to Roundington\". </p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>FastPack</i> <i>- Quick Delivery Training Program</i> is a fast paced game where you deliver packages to the correct adress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697540/extras/2109030245f6fdbe8fe7775f9cdcf7d0.poster.avif?t=1751833217\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2697540/extras/2109030245f6fdbe8fe7775f9cdcf7d0.webm?t=1751833217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced package delivery</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drive around in a small open world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Talk to strange NPC's</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise your profile</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn a Diploma you can print out and put next to your CV</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade mode:</strong> Deliver packages as fast as possible in a race against the clock. Gain more time by delivering more packages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Contract Mode:</strong> Walk around without time constraint. Complete contracts to gain Money. Contracts are small missions, for example \"Deliver 20 packages to Roundington\". </p></li></ul>",
